          <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Symbols</text> of Kinematic-element and sketch-elements are on the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Mechanism-Plane</text>. </li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joint</text> - the <text styleclass="VariableName-small" style="color:#ff0000;">only</text> kinematic-element that can be offset from the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Mechanism-Plane</text>. </li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Interface">MD</text><text styleclass="Popup Box2">-Solids</text> extrude perpendicular to the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Mechanism-Plane</text>. </li>
          </list>
